WEBVTT

00:09.600 --> 00:11.040
This is Uncle's keepsake,

00:11.840 --> 00:13.841
and also an old item belonging
to Your Majesty.

00:14.481 --> 00:15.361
Until his death,

00:17.520 --> 00:19.321
he held it tightly in his hand.

00:20.388 --> 00:22.401
If there's any suspicion
surrounding his death,

00:22.560 --> 00:24.521
I ask Your Majesty
to investigate thoroughly.

00:42.641 --> 00:45.680
Meisun, I remember the Grand Mentor
was strict with me

00:45.681 --> 00:47.079
(Young Emperor. Young Duke of Ding)
when we were studying back then.

00:47.080 --> 00:50.091
(Young Emperor. Young Duke of Ding)
And you had all the freedom you wanted.

00:52.521 --> 00:54.079
I even remember that one time

00:54.080 --> 00:55.920
I asked you to sneak me
out of the palace.

00:55.921 --> 00:57.000
Father was furious

00:57.001 --> 00:58.960
and locked you up for days.

00:59.641 --> 01:03.081
You were always protecting me
at the time.

01:04.601 --> 01:06.120
It was your idea

01:06.121 --> 01:07.720
but I was the one getting punished.

01:08.481 --> 01:11.160
Time passes so quickly.

01:13.041 --> 01:14.800
Now, you're the emperor

01:15.041 --> 01:17.520
and it's my duty to serve the country
and the throne.

01:21.520 --> 01:22.321
Meisun,

01:24.201 --> 01:25.080
I'm lucky

01:25.880 --> 01:27.401
to have you around.

01:32.600 --> 01:33.321
See there?

01:33.701 --> 01:35.760
Once we've reclaimed
the lost lands in the north,

01:35.761 --> 01:37.640
we'll go there to watch the sunrise.

01:37.641 --> 01:39.840
We haven't dealt with the pirates
in the southeast yet.

01:39.841 --> 01:41.121
How can we focus on the north?

01:41.160 --> 01:43.171
Even if we could reclaim
the north in the future,

01:43.181 --> 01:45.879
or you're not afraid of my achievements
overshadowing the throne,

01:45.880 --> 01:48.691
I still fear you would accuse me
of deceiving and betraying the emperor.

01:48.701 --> 01:49.800
Don't get started with that.

01:50.681 --> 01:51.961
Back in the Eastern Palace,

01:52.121 --> 01:55.201
the Grand Mentor taught me
how to rule with this ruler.

01:55.320 --> 01:57.159
Now that the Grand Mentor
has passed away,

01:57.160 --> 01:59.761
I would still need you
to set me straight with this ruler

01:59.960 --> 02:02.481
if I start making foolish decisions
in the future.

02:03.121 --> 02:03.881
Jiang Meisun.

02:04.240 --> 02:05.359
Yes, Your Majesty.

02:05.360 --> 02:08.121
I'm granting you a special status.

02:08.320 --> 02:10.960
You can enter the palace fully armed,
need not bow before me,

02:11.001 --> 02:13.400
and no hierarchy between us.

02:13.401 --> 02:15.841
Let alone the question
of deceiving and betraying the emperor.

02:17.681 --> 02:21.800
If Your Majesty makes a mistake
in the future, I won't hold back.

02:24.001 --> 02:25.001
Uncle always said

02:25.320 --> 02:27.120
his biggest wish in life

02:27.361 --> 02:29.080
was to pacify the pirates

02:29.561 --> 02:30.921
and return to the capital

02:31.920 --> 02:33.680
to have a proper chat with Your Majesty.

02:34.681 --> 02:38.001
He's been saying that for fifteen years.

02:38.480 --> 02:40.241
His feelings remained the same.

02:41.801 --> 02:43.240
But when did

02:44.681 --> 02:46.881
Your Majesty's heart start to change?

02:48.760 --> 02:51.520
Or is it that the heart

02:52.760 --> 02:54.840
of an emperor can't trust anyone?

02:55.361 --> 02:56.080
Insolence!

02:56.760 --> 02:57.721
Your Majesty.

02:59.401 --> 03:00.401
Your Majesty.

03:02.241 --> 03:03.120
Find out

03:05.841 --> 03:07.321
who tortured

03:08.640 --> 03:10.680
and killed Meisun.

03:13.040 --> 03:13.840
Your Majesty.

03:15.081 --> 03:17.920
Do not spare any one of them!

03:18.640 --> 03:19.960
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

03:19.961 --> 03:24.680
- Your Majesty! Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

03:24.681 --> 03:26.191
- Hurry! Your Majesty!
- Your Majesty!

03:26.201 --> 03:27.721
Send Official Lu here quickly!

03:28.160 --> 03:29.081
Your Majesty.

03:29.440 --> 03:31.360
Take this rebellious brat away

03:31.440 --> 03:32.800
from here!

03:32.801 --> 03:34.421
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

04:55.501 --> 04:59.500
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

04:59.501 --> 05:02.621
=Episode 8=

05:04.241 --> 05:05.040
Mother.

05:05.561 --> 05:06.441
Bring it over.

05:16.760 --> 05:17.681
How is she?

05:21.141 --> 05:22.199
All of you can leave now.

05:22.200 --> 05:23.040
Go.

05:23.760 --> 05:24.640
Go.

05:36.520 --> 05:38.480
I've talked to everyone in the capital

05:38.681 --> 05:40.080
who has any say in this.

05:40.440 --> 05:43.319
Luckily, His Majesty
regained consciousness in time.

05:43.320 --> 05:45.720
Otherwise, the entire Song Clan

05:45.721 --> 05:48.600
would likely be doomed.

05:49.361 --> 05:51.321
What about the officials' memorials?

05:51.520 --> 05:53.361
Especially
the Grand Secretariat's stance.

05:55.840 --> 05:57.321
I can take it.

05:58.440 --> 05:59.561
All right.

05:59.681 --> 06:01.040
Don't get agitated.

06:01.400 --> 06:02.798
There are still some people

06:02.799 --> 06:04.959
who defend the Duke of Ding
and Yantang.

06:04.960 --> 06:06.561
But some say

06:06.840 --> 06:08.519
that though the Duke of Ding is dead,

06:08.520 --> 06:10.480
his army still remains.

06:10.801 --> 06:14.600
Now, Yantang has become
the heart of the Ding Army.

06:14.840 --> 06:16.959
He's even barged into the palace

06:16.960 --> 06:18.160
and rebuked His Majesty.

06:18.520 --> 06:21.761
What if he ever rises up in rebellion
to seek revenge?

06:25.241 --> 06:27.001
If we don't deal with it properly now,

06:27.481 --> 06:29.600
the consequences will be disastrous.

06:33.041 --> 06:35.921
His Majesty
may have regained consciousness.

06:36.121 --> 06:39.840
But he hasn't said a word
about Yantang's sentencing.

06:40.960 --> 06:46.201
We can only gamble
on His Majesty's decision for now.

06:49.840 --> 06:50.801
Preserved fruits.

06:51.801 --> 06:52.561
Give me one.

06:58.640 --> 06:59.280
Slowly.

07:04.121 --> 07:05.639
Why hasn't the new prescription shown

07:05.640 --> 07:07.241
any improvement?

07:10.721 --> 07:11.441
Someone!

07:11.960 --> 07:13.468
Make sure the lady's medicine is brewed

07:13.469 --> 07:14.721
with a stronger dose.

07:22.361 --> 07:23.639
Those in Futing have heard

07:23.640 --> 07:25.640
about the Marshal's death.

07:26.080 --> 07:27.561
If anything happens to Lord Song,

07:27.721 --> 07:29.161
the army's morale will collapse.

07:30.400 --> 07:32.839
Dou Shishu and his students
have been impeaching him nonstop.

07:32.840 --> 07:34.720
If something happens to Lord Song,

07:34.721 --> 07:36.681
I'll have the entire
Dou Family wiped out!

07:39.161 --> 07:40.001
General Yan,

07:40.241 --> 07:41.801
don't stay at this manor anymore

07:41.840 --> 07:43.401
and follow me to the capital.

07:43.520 --> 07:45.240
With our brothers from the Ding Army,

07:45.241 --> 07:46.600
it might still be possible

07:46.760 --> 07:48.801
to save Lord Song
if we try to break him out.

07:49.681 --> 07:51.480
Lord Song has yet to be convicted.

07:51.481 --> 07:52.600
If you do this,

07:53.161 --> 07:54.480
it will be treason for real.

07:55.601 --> 07:57.251
Even if the prison break succeeds,

07:57.261 --> 07:58.960
what about the lives
of hundreds of people

07:58.961 --> 08:01.241
from the Jiang and Song Clan?

08:01.801 --> 08:03.400
Lord Song is in this situation

08:03.520 --> 08:06.160
because you tricked him with your words!

08:06.481 --> 08:08.081
If you dare to interfere again...

08:12.200 --> 08:14.800
Rebelling against the emperor
and damaging the ruler's dignity.

08:14.801 --> 08:17.040
According to the law,
that's punishable by death.

08:17.520 --> 08:19.079
His Majesty hasn't dealt with it yet.

08:19.080 --> 08:22.161
The Grand Secretariat has been debating
the punishment for days with no result.

08:22.481 --> 08:24.681
Why do you think that happens,
General Yan?

08:31.001 --> 08:33.679
His Majesty knows
the Marshal died unjustly

08:33.680 --> 08:35.760
and is trying
to test the court's loyalty

08:36.201 --> 08:37.960
by questioning Lord Song's case.

08:38.121 --> 08:39.281
That's the first reason.

08:39.601 --> 08:41.241
As long as the emperor feels guilty,

08:41.961 --> 08:43.960
the power struggles in the court

08:44.640 --> 08:46.921
will be handled
by Grand Secretary Wu and Wang Xingyi.

08:47.920 --> 08:49.120
What about the second reason?

08:49.121 --> 08:51.600
No matter how much His Majesty
values the Duke of Ding,

08:51.601 --> 08:53.441
no one can resurrect a dead man.

08:53.560 --> 08:55.601
Song Mo, the living one,
is the variable.

08:55.721 --> 08:57.120
If you break him out of prison,

08:57.400 --> 08:59.120
it will turn

08:59.241 --> 09:01.521
His Majesty's loyal
and filial Young General

09:01.800 --> 09:04.480
into a hateful rebel.

09:07.201 --> 09:09.639
His Majesty has already sent
the Ministry of Imperial Ceremony

09:09.640 --> 09:12.000
to Futing to investigate
the Duke of Ding's death.

09:12.901 --> 09:15.181
Even the Earl of Yunyang
couldn't obtain any information

09:15.182 --> 09:16.760
from the Ministry of Imperial Ceremony.

09:17.280 --> 09:19.240
How did you know about it?

09:19.721 --> 09:22.559
General Yan, you have been staying
at my residence for several days.

09:22.560 --> 09:23.600
You should know

09:23.601 --> 09:25.681
I do not only have business in Futing.

09:25.961 --> 09:28.601
I have long-standing clients
among high officials in the capital.

09:28.800 --> 09:30.000
There are plenty of ways

09:30.081 --> 09:31.161
to gather information.

09:32.560 --> 09:33.960
Of course, I hope

09:33.961 --> 09:36.000
that you're on our side.

09:36.920 --> 09:37.921
If so,

09:38.680 --> 09:40.041
here's the deal,

09:40.601 --> 09:43.161
you'll follow us to the capital
and rescue Lord Song.

09:43.520 --> 09:45.321
Once he's safely out of prison,

09:46.081 --> 09:48.281
you can have Mr. Chen back.

09:49.520 --> 09:53.521
Otherwise, Mr. Chen and I
will die together.

09:54.680 --> 09:56.041
I won't be alone too.

09:56.121 --> 09:56.801
No.

09:56.961 --> 09:58.159
This is too dangerous.

09:58.160 --> 09:59.841
It's precisely because it's dangerous.

10:00.081 --> 10:02.161
I know you value loyalty

10:02.400 --> 10:04.200
and wouldn't let Mr. Chen die

10:04.201 --> 10:05.641
with us, right?

10:07.920 --> 10:09.201
We're allies.

10:10.520 --> 10:13.401
It's our obligation to save Lord Song.

10:14.680 --> 10:17.600
But you threatened me in such a manner.

10:18.520 --> 10:20.401
So that changes things.

10:23.800 --> 10:26.641
I'm only a soldier.

10:27.241 --> 10:29.201
So my actions and words
are far from elegant.

10:29.241 --> 10:32.240
Fourth Young Lady, as an ally,

10:32.361 --> 10:33.561
please save Lord Song.

10:35.280 --> 10:38.600
Please come with us and save Lord Song.

10:42.560 --> 10:43.880
I will accept

10:44.441 --> 10:45.240
your request.

10:48.061 --> 10:53.421
(Zhaowen Bookstore)

10:53.680 --> 10:54.360
Young Lady,

10:54.361 --> 10:56.679
threatening us with Mr. Chen
is not the act of a gentleman.

10:56.680 --> 10:58.080
Besides, this is a risky mission.

10:58.081 --> 11:00.120
I don't want Lord Song to die either.

11:01.881 --> 11:02.519
(Zhao Liangbi)
Young Lady.

11:02.520 --> 11:03.401
(Zhaowen Bookstore Manager)
Mr. Zhao.

11:03.481 --> 11:04.679
I came here unexpectedly.

11:04.680 --> 11:06.040
We've prepared everything needed.

11:06.041 --> 11:08.500
For some news, we'll have to wait
for another one or two days.

11:08.501 --> 11:09.960
It's just a few small paper shops.

11:09.961 --> 11:11.960
They're acting
like they have spies everywhere.

11:12.040 --> 11:13.080
General Yan,

11:13.121 --> 11:14.880
this is about Lord Song's life.

11:16.441 --> 11:17.600
This way, General Yan.

11:55.401 --> 11:57.640
These goods are
for the Ministry of Imperial Ceremony.

11:57.641 --> 12:00.121
The profit margin may be small.
But the quantity is large.

12:02.040 --> 12:03.120
The real money comes

12:03.241 --> 12:04.201
from this scrap paper.

12:04.211 --> 12:07.601
Young Lady's idea was to collect scrap paper
from all the residences in the capital.

12:07.611 --> 12:08.880
After pulping and grinding it down,

12:08.881 --> 12:11.101
we make it into toilet paper
and sell it to various residents.

12:11.101 --> 12:13.480
The better-quality paper,
mixed with lime and scented oil,

12:13.520 --> 12:15.000
goes to the palace's Paper Office.

12:15.721 --> 12:16.600
This way,

12:16.800 --> 12:19.201
all the news from the palace,
the ministries, the ministers,

12:19.520 --> 12:20.720
and various shops

12:21.121 --> 12:24.000
are all connected.

12:27.680 --> 12:30.120
You're actually supplying

12:31.680 --> 12:33.480
nearly all the paper used
in the capital.

12:33.680 --> 12:35.720
But that's not the point here.

12:36.400 --> 12:37.921
General Yan, please follow me.

12:45.201 --> 12:46.441
Wisteria paper?

12:46.481 --> 12:48.201
It's only regular paper.

12:51.721 --> 12:53.000
But in this world,

12:53.160 --> 12:55.720
only the emperor and Grand Secretariat
use wisteria paper

12:56.800 --> 12:58.681
to write memorials and petitions.

13:00.001 --> 13:03.201
Your business even reached the emperor.

13:04.680 --> 13:05.641
In business,

13:06.280 --> 13:08.401
the most important thing is honesty.

13:09.001 --> 13:12.000
Once you know someone's ability,
you'll know if they are trustworthy.

13:19.731 --> 13:21.759
The physicians
who have been treating His Majesty

13:21.760 --> 13:22.771
returned home last night.

13:22.771 --> 13:23.991
His Majesty's health is stable.

13:25.001 --> 13:27.991
The officials and the Grand Secretariat
have been at a standstill for days.

13:28.321 --> 13:30.921
But His Majesty still hasn't issued
a verdict.

13:32.040 --> 13:33.445
Things would be much easier

13:33.446 --> 13:36.519
if we could just get a hint
of His Majesty's intentions.

13:36.520 --> 13:38.600
Does that mean we just wait

13:38.640 --> 13:40.961
and let Lord Song's fate
in prison remain uncertain?

13:41.001 --> 13:43.441
You've been with Lord Song
for over ten years.

13:44.400 --> 13:46.281
He's not someone who just sits back

13:46.601 --> 13:48.000
and waits to die.

13:48.201 --> 13:49.480
Before he barged into the palace,

13:49.481 --> 13:51.841
he must have already figured out
a way to break through.

13:52.300 --> 13:53.860
If you ask me,

13:54.021 --> 13:56.380
since His Majesty fell ill
and started recovering,

13:56.501 --> 13:58.020
he still hasn't sentenced Song Mo.

13:58.420 --> 14:00.401
This shows
His Majesty doesn't want to kill him.

14:00.820 --> 14:03.541
We should hear something
from the palace within three days.

14:04.700 --> 14:06.819
So let's all wait a little longer.

14:06.820 --> 14:08.201
That's the Imperial Prison.

14:08.861 --> 14:10.500
Those who killed the Marshal

14:10.501 --> 14:13.260
will do everything they can
to make sure Lord Song dies in there.

14:13.460 --> 14:14.860
I've already come up with a plan

14:14.940 --> 14:16.341
and sent Su Lan to handle it.

14:17.080 --> 14:18.321
Just be patient a bit longer.

14:26.242 --> 14:27.202
That's enough.

14:34.202 --> 14:37.721
What you did is a capital offense.

14:38.281 --> 14:39.922
To the court officials,

14:40.442 --> 14:42.601
it looks like you
and your uncle are in this together,

14:42.962 --> 14:45.081
and it's hard to avoid
suspicion of treason.

14:46.761 --> 14:48.802
If you write a confession,

14:49.082 --> 14:52.601
give in, and admit your mistake
to His Majesty,

14:53.122 --> 14:55.361
you might have a chance
to plead for mercy.

14:57.002 --> 14:58.162
Don't you agree?

15:01.681 --> 15:04.241
There are 720 pressure points
in the human body

15:04.921 --> 15:06.802
and 78 joints.

15:08.322 --> 15:10.562
He doesn't even know
where it hurts the most.

15:11.561 --> 15:12.481
Eunuch Wang,

15:13.281 --> 15:15.642
do you need my help
to teach your subordinate?

15:18.401 --> 15:19.282
I see.

15:29.322 --> 15:32.761
It seems there's no point
in saying more.

15:34.002 --> 15:35.802
It's time for things to get serious now.

15:38.681 --> 15:40.361
Is this really necessary to be jailed

15:40.362 --> 15:41.881
for such a petty crime?

15:47.561 --> 15:48.642
Eunuch Wang,

15:49.122 --> 15:50.241
are you using torture?

15:51.681 --> 15:52.880
Sorry to disturb you.

15:52.881 --> 15:53.881
You can continue.

15:54.641 --> 15:56.961
I'll just watch from here. Go on.

16:01.681 --> 16:02.481
Earl of Yunyang,

16:02.482 --> 16:03.761
why are you...

16:07.641 --> 16:08.841
Look what I have here.

16:09.482 --> 16:11.802
The official paper
the Court of Judicial Review issued.

16:12.161 --> 16:14.241
There's nothing I can do

16:14.242 --> 16:16.361
if the Court of Judicial Review wants
to imprison me.

16:16.362 --> 16:17.721
Song Mo's treason is clear

16:17.722 --> 16:18.961
and death is inevitable.

16:19.322 --> 16:20.282
Are you going

16:21.122 --> 16:22.642
to die along with him?

16:23.082 --> 16:24.881
What's wrong with me wanting to?

16:25.401 --> 16:26.642
You won't let me into prison.

16:27.281 --> 16:28.562
Are there no laws anymore?

16:29.722 --> 16:31.761
Let's go to my aunt's place
and reason this out.

16:35.082 --> 16:36.642
As long as you want this.

16:46.202 --> 16:47.162
Open the door.

16:58.561 --> 17:00.961
These servants dared to go this far.

17:02.041 --> 17:03.522
Luckily, I brought the medicine.

17:03.921 --> 17:05.882
Where's the medicine box? Bring it in!

17:07.561 --> 17:08.481
How is

17:09.882 --> 17:10.961
His Majesty?

17:14.361 --> 17:15.561
He woke up two days ago.

17:15.761 --> 17:17.001
But he still needs to rest.

17:18.121 --> 17:19.362
I tried to see him.

17:20.521 --> 17:22.082
But my aunt sent me away.

17:22.682 --> 17:24.642
Mr. Wu and the others
didn't get to see him.

17:24.722 --> 17:26.442
Even the Crown Prince was scolded

17:26.521 --> 17:27.842
when he went to tend to him.

17:31.121 --> 17:32.801
How did you manage to get in?

17:34.081 --> 17:34.961
Easy.

17:35.442 --> 17:36.922
I picked on someone I didn't like

17:37.281 --> 17:38.162
and beat him up.

17:47.561 --> 17:49.321
Who hit me?

17:50.682 --> 17:51.521
Me.

17:55.281 --> 17:56.922
You're too caught up in the situation.

17:57.242 --> 17:59.682
Even your female teacher sees things
more clearly than you do.

18:00.521 --> 18:01.642
Female teacher?

18:02.841 --> 18:05.281
You mean Fourth Young Lady Dou?

18:05.601 --> 18:06.761
She sent you here?

18:07.081 --> 18:07.842
Yes.

18:07.962 --> 18:09.332
Or else I would not have come here.

18:09.342 --> 18:11.760
I've been running around Qianqing Palace
like a headless chicken.

18:11.761 --> 18:13.472
Aunt keeps avoiding
and refusing to see me.

18:13.472 --> 18:15.560
Aunt. Song Mo didn't mean
to disrespect the emperor.

18:15.561 --> 18:18.120
He did it out of loyalty
and filial piety. Please spare him this time.

18:18.121 --> 18:19.120
- Send him away.
- Aunt!

18:19.121 --> 18:20.432
He won't do it again!

18:20.442 --> 18:21.001
Aunt!

18:21.002 --> 18:22.801
All thanks to a eunuch
from the Paper Office

18:22.802 --> 18:24.442
who delivered me this embroidered pouch.

18:24.922 --> 18:26.481
He said a lady from a bookstore gave it.

18:27.801 --> 18:30.760
I can tell the only one who could come up
with this idea

18:30.761 --> 18:32.281
is that female teacher of yours.

18:34.321 --> 18:36.241
(Stay in prison after request papers from the Court of Judicial Review.)
She told you to remain in prison

18:36.242 --> 18:38.280
after requesting for official paper
from the Court of Judicial Review?

18:38.281 --> 18:39.241
Yes.

18:39.761 --> 18:41.122
As long as I'm here,

18:41.442 --> 18:43.162
no one would dare to harm you.

18:47.321 --> 18:48.202
Do you really think

18:48.801 --> 18:51.041
she would dare send this out

18:51.921 --> 18:53.602
with her "exceptional" embroidery skills?

18:59.121 --> 19:00.122
This embroidery

19:00.922 --> 19:02.041
is quite unique.

19:02.482 --> 19:03.281
Tell me

19:03.801 --> 19:04.801
what this is.

19:10.442 --> 19:12.521
She's mocking me.

19:13.761 --> 19:15.842
At a time
when half the court wants you dead,

19:16.292 --> 19:18.560
she had the eunuch
from the Paper Office deliver things.

19:18.561 --> 19:20.602
That's a task that puts lives at risk.

19:21.722 --> 19:23.082
Anyone who helps you like this

19:23.482 --> 19:24.721
is truly a person of chivalry.

19:28.742 --> 19:32.422
(Zhaowen Bookstore)

19:33.162 --> 19:34.082
Sir.

19:34.801 --> 19:35.602
This is...

19:36.402 --> 19:37.281
Keep it safe.

19:41.482 --> 19:44.082
I cannot help with matters
like the embroidered pouch again.

19:44.361 --> 19:47.161
Over the last couple of days,
His Majesty has only met with Mr. Wu

19:47.162 --> 19:48.982
and some officials
from the Grand Secretariat.

19:49.402 --> 19:52.320
Most of the time,
he either writes his official decrees

19:52.321 --> 19:54.481
or stares blankly at that broken ruler.

19:55.162 --> 19:56.281
Beyond that,

19:56.402 --> 19:58.001
I'm afraid I can't say more.

19:59.801 --> 20:00.922
Thank you, sir.

20:01.002 --> 20:01.761
All right.

20:07.841 --> 20:08.602
Young Lady.

20:20.602 --> 20:22.707
The enemy is in the dark,
but we are in the light.

20:22.708 --> 20:24.162
We can't afford to wait any longer!

20:26.202 --> 20:27.842
I've already had my men set up an ambush

20:27.843 --> 20:29.401
around the Northern Pacification Bureau.

20:29.402 --> 20:31.922
Fireworks will signal the time,
and we'll act at midnight.

20:32.561 --> 20:33.602
General Yan,

20:34.242 --> 20:35.560
please wait one more day.

20:35.561 --> 20:37.120
We've waited for three days.

20:37.121 --> 20:38.441
Do we still have to wait?

20:38.442 --> 20:40.281
Are you planning

20:40.361 --> 20:41.642
to delay us on purpose?

20:43.361 --> 20:45.122
The situation has already turned around.

20:45.522 --> 20:46.921
His life is hanging by the thread.

20:46.922 --> 20:48.082
We cannot wait anymore.

20:48.162 --> 20:49.362
We must save Lord Song.

20:49.371 --> 20:51.840
You will only send
Lord Song to his death. A bunch of fools.

20:51.841 --> 20:52.532
What did you say?

20:52.542 --> 20:54.302
She said, your foolishness
is beyond saved.

20:54.312 --> 20:54.481
You!

20:54.482 --> 20:55.202
Enough.

20:55.321 --> 20:56.842
Since you want to save Lord Song.

20:57.962 --> 20:59.521
I'll show you something.

21:08.081 --> 21:08.842
Stay still!

21:09.642 --> 21:10.481
Dou Zhao,

21:10.641 --> 21:11.760
what's the meaning of this?

21:11.761 --> 21:13.772
I'm tired.
I don't want to waste time explaining.

21:13.782 --> 21:15.001
Lock them in the coal shed.

21:15.081 --> 21:15.481
You!

21:15.482 --> 21:16.321
Dou Zhao!

21:16.521 --> 21:17.881
My apologies, gentlemen.

21:17.882 --> 21:18.682
Move it!

21:20.402 --> 21:21.441
Quickly now!

21:21.442 --> 21:22.122
Move!

21:28.162 --> 21:29.721
As the head of the Ministry of Rites,

21:29.722 --> 21:31.922
you should have entered
the Grand Secretariat by now.

21:32.521 --> 21:34.082
But Official Wu feels

21:34.521 --> 21:35.961
you're still too inexperienced.

21:37.162 --> 21:40.281
Since he's the one in charge
of the Grand Secretariat.

21:42.162 --> 21:43.362
You must understand that.

21:45.962 --> 21:47.280
I really have no accomplishments

21:47.281 --> 21:48.321
to convince them.

21:48.841 --> 21:50.881
Official Wu is experienced and wise.

21:50.882 --> 21:52.162
I completely agree with him.

21:54.162 --> 21:56.082
Grand Princess Shude once said

21:56.402 --> 21:58.561
you are a versatile talent.

21:58.642 --> 22:00.082
I will definitely use you.

22:00.922 --> 22:02.162
For example,

22:03.002 --> 22:05.481
Song Mo is awaiting trial
in prison right now.

22:06.321 --> 22:08.040
The six ministries and nine ministers,

22:08.041 --> 22:09.442
including your students,

22:09.642 --> 22:13.162
are all sending petitions
for his death sentence.

22:13.841 --> 22:15.162
What do you think of this?

22:22.281 --> 22:24.442
Song Mo is a renowned general,

22:24.642 --> 22:26.120
known for his victories.

22:26.121 --> 22:28.602
No one among the younger generation
can match him.

22:29.642 --> 22:32.481
If we kill such a pillar of the court,

22:32.482 --> 22:34.362
it will certainly demoralize
the Three Armies.

22:34.402 --> 22:36.721
But the Ding Army has been stationed

22:36.801 --> 22:38.082
in Futing for too long

22:38.162 --> 22:39.681
and is beyond the court's control.

22:39.682 --> 22:40.881
They've become reckless,

22:40.882 --> 22:43.082
even leaving the camp without decree

22:43.281 --> 22:45.481
and coming to the capital.

22:53.642 --> 22:55.001
I mean,

22:56.041 --> 22:58.561
even if Song Mo has been disrespectful,

22:58.882 --> 23:01.001
he is likely being provoked
by his subordinates.

23:07.281 --> 23:10.122
So we have to deal with the trouble
at its source.

23:11.002 --> 23:13.561
I'll let you handle this matter.

23:15.642 --> 23:17.281
I shall comply, Your Majesty.

23:20.242 --> 23:24.442
By the will of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees,

23:24.561 --> 23:26.521
the auspicious signs are here.

23:26.801 --> 23:29.281
The era name is changed to "Fengming."

23:29.521 --> 23:30.842
Today, a special pardon

23:30.882 --> 23:33.402
is granted to Song Mo,
the legitimate son of Duke of Ying,

23:33.482 --> 23:36.162
and Gu Yu, the Earl of Yunyang.

23:36.682 --> 23:40.402
Song Mo is removed
from his military duties

23:40.561 --> 23:43.561
and expected to reflect on your actions.

23:43.642 --> 23:45.362
This is the emperor's will.

23:59.761 --> 24:00.602
Eunuch Wang,

24:00.882 --> 24:01.882
why a special pardon?

24:03.922 --> 24:06.001
Do you not know?

24:06.521 --> 24:08.761
Today, His Majesty held a grand ceremony

24:08.882 --> 24:10.481
to announce the change in era

24:10.482 --> 24:11.801
and grant amnesty to all.

24:12.202 --> 24:14.801
Thus, a special pardon.

24:16.402 --> 24:18.122
But what about Duke of Ding's injustice?

24:18.682 --> 24:21.122
What about the Jiang Clan's fate?

24:22.601 --> 24:25.481
The Jiang Family is spared from death

24:25.521 --> 24:26.922
but demoted to commoners.

24:27.041 --> 24:28.681
The men will be exiled to Tieling,

24:28.682 --> 24:31.642
and the women and children
will be sent back to their homeland.

24:32.081 --> 24:34.842
His Majesty has been very merciful.

24:35.041 --> 24:36.001
Lord Song,

24:36.561 --> 24:38.041
go home and recuperate.

24:50.162 --> 24:51.641
Since you've been pardoned,

24:51.642 --> 24:53.522
I'm sure your parents
will come to pick you up.

24:54.601 --> 24:55.201
Your Lordship.

24:55.202 --> 24:57.092
(Lyu Zheng, Butler
in Duke of Ying's Residence)

24:57.102 --> 24:58.481
The Duke can't come in person.

24:58.521 --> 25:01.281
Please return quickly.

25:03.962 --> 25:05.281
Tell my parents

25:05.321 --> 25:06.642
that I'll return on my own.

25:08.162 --> 25:09.202
Yes, Your Lordship.

25:16.402 --> 25:19.602
I've become a disgrace
to the Duke of Ying's family.

25:20.121 --> 25:21.561
I should keep a low profile.

25:32.002 --> 25:33.561
This is General Yan's signal.

25:35.482 --> 25:37.521
This very signal almost cost you,
your life.

25:38.242 --> 25:39.761
Once the fireworks are set off,

25:40.402 --> 25:42.202
it will be an appropriate time
for action.

25:45.561 --> 25:46.402
Where is she?

25:47.162 --> 25:48.001
Lord Song,

25:48.402 --> 25:49.402
come this way.

26:09.962 --> 26:12.561
How did you know I would be pardoned
and released from prison?

26:13.041 --> 26:14.521
Information from the Paper Office.

26:15.602 --> 26:18.041
His Majesty has been writing
official decrees day and night,

26:18.042 --> 26:19.561
burning incense, and paying respects.

26:19.562 --> 26:21.842
He places that broken ruler on the desk.

26:22.482 --> 26:25.001
It shows that his remorse
for Duke of Ding's death

26:25.281 --> 26:27.162
is greater than his suspicions.

26:27.482 --> 26:29.041
That's why he won't kill you.

26:30.722 --> 26:32.321
Why wait until today, though?

26:32.922 --> 26:35.402
Because today marks
the seventh day of Uncle's death.

26:38.521 --> 26:40.241
Dou Shishu and his followers

26:40.281 --> 26:41.962
have been impeaching me every day.

26:42.561 --> 26:44.802
You used an embroidered pouch
to have Gu Yu protect me.

26:45.761 --> 26:47.602
What exactly are you trying
to achieve here?

26:47.801 --> 26:50.162
This is a business deal
between me and General Yan.

26:50.521 --> 26:52.001
Since you are safe now,

26:52.321 --> 26:54.402
I hope we can settle our affairs soon.

27:07.041 --> 27:08.280
I've already instructed my men

27:08.281 --> 27:10.321
to release General Yan and his men.

27:10.761 --> 27:12.642
I ask that you keep your promise

27:13.041 --> 27:14.442
and return Mr. Chen to me.

27:23.081 --> 27:24.281
You went

27:26.121 --> 27:27.962
against your uncle only for this reason?

27:40.002 --> 27:43.001
Even fireworks come in different colors.

27:44.162 --> 27:46.801
My uncle and I are different.

27:53.761 --> 27:54.602
Thank you.

27:56.801 --> 27:57.842
What did you say?

27:58.482 --> 28:00.002
I didn't hear that clearly.

28:05.841 --> 28:06.721
I said,

28:08.882 --> 28:09.842
thank you.

28:12.442 --> 28:13.681
The fireworks are too loud.

28:13.682 --> 28:15.162
I still can't hear it clearly.

28:15.202 --> 28:17.882
Can you repeat that, Lord Song?

28:18.002 --> 28:19.121
I heard it loud and clear.

28:19.122 --> 28:20.642
He said he likes you.

28:20.722 --> 28:21.442
Shut up.

28:25.922 --> 28:27.120
He didn't hear it clearly.

28:27.121 --> 28:28.201
Ah, yes. I misheard it.

28:28.202 --> 28:29.682
He said he wants to marry you!

28:31.761 --> 28:32.120
Shut up.

28:32.121 --> 28:33.362
Stop spouting nonsense.

28:34.002 --> 28:35.722
I'll wait for your good news at home.

28:50.602 --> 28:52.282
No words can express how thankful I am.

28:52.452 --> 28:54.840
I'm hosting a banquet
at Guanghe Tower the following night.

28:54.841 --> 28:56.922
I hope you will grace us
with your presence.

28:57.202 --> 29:00.122
I'll also return Mr. Chen to you
at that time.

29:18.761 --> 29:19.561
Your Lordship.

29:20.081 --> 29:20.882
Your Lordship.

29:22.041 --> 29:24.001
- Your Lordship.
- Your Lordship.

29:25.761 --> 29:26.642
You're...

29:27.242 --> 29:28.162
What happened?

29:30.041 --> 29:32.761
The boys were worried about your safety

29:32.801 --> 29:34.481
and wanted to break into the prison.

29:34.482 --> 29:36.652
But Fourth Young Lady managed
to talk them out of it.

29:36.662 --> 29:37.612
She talked us out of it?

29:37.622 --> 29:38.202
Quiet.

29:41.081 --> 29:43.241
Entering the prison
was a form of self-sacrifice.

29:43.441 --> 29:46.041
I was betting His Majesty feels guilty
about Duke of Ding's death.

29:46.042 --> 29:47.961
So he would show mercy
to the Jiang Family.

29:50.962 --> 29:51.961
She figured it out.

29:52.242 --> 29:53.241
But you didn't see it?

29:55.642 --> 29:56.402
I admit

29:56.962 --> 29:58.241
we were reckless.

29:59.882 --> 30:02.602
I'll go and receive
twenty lashes as punishment.

30:03.002 --> 30:03.761
I'll go too.

30:03.801 --> 30:04.561
Me too.

30:05.962 --> 30:08.721
It happened because you were worried.
So forget about the punishment.

30:08.722 --> 30:11.082
No, thanks.
I'll go and receive my punishment now.

30:15.162 --> 30:16.882
Go after you wash your face.

30:21.882 --> 30:24.402
It's very late.
How about you go back inside first?

30:36.642 --> 30:37.281
Mo,

30:37.722 --> 30:39.201
I hunted this wild deer for you.

30:39.202 --> 30:41.682
The antlers are perfect for your health.

30:47.922 --> 30:49.241
How is Mother's condition?

30:49.642 --> 30:51.082
Father is taking care of her.

31:08.442 --> 31:09.922
You don't want to get involved.

31:10.121 --> 31:13.041
But don't forget, I'm also a Jiang.

31:13.682 --> 31:15.561
I'm not looking down on you.

31:15.682 --> 31:17.161
Yantang is lucky

31:17.162 --> 31:18.800
to survive.

31:18.801 --> 31:21.321
Now, many eyes are on this matter.

31:21.682 --> 31:23.560
So you would
put the Jiang Family's safety

31:23.561 --> 31:25.561
above the Song Family's?

31:26.841 --> 31:27.642
Mo.

31:30.482 --> 31:34.402
Do you want me to sever ties
with the Jiang Family?

31:34.722 --> 31:35.721
Let me send it.

31:36.281 --> 31:38.241
That's not my intention.

31:38.242 --> 31:40.320
It's just
that the situation is still unstable.

31:40.321 --> 31:42.842
So we must be cautious
with our words and actions.

31:44.882 --> 31:45.721
Come in.

31:52.041 --> 31:54.122
Father. Mother.

31:55.882 --> 31:56.961
I've acted recklessly

31:57.962 --> 31:59.281
and made you worry.

32:02.242 --> 32:03.600
You really need to change

32:03.601 --> 32:05.120
your arrogant and reckless nature.

32:05.121 --> 32:07.080
Look at what you've done to your mother.

32:07.081 --> 32:09.082
She hasn't had a full night's rest
in days.

32:18.402 --> 32:19.202
Mother.

32:19.402 --> 32:20.202
Mo.

32:21.162 --> 32:22.561
You look so worn out.

32:23.922 --> 32:25.682
Your...

32:29.402 --> 32:30.202
This...

32:34.321 --> 32:35.402
Let me see.

32:37.642 --> 32:39.202
The Shadow Guard's methods

32:40.521 --> 32:42.001
are lethal.

32:42.361 --> 32:43.882
It's just for show.

32:44.302 --> 32:46.402
No one would truly dare
to make things hard for me.

32:46.601 --> 32:49.162
Forgive me for making you worried.

32:49.442 --> 32:51.082
But seeing what happened to Uncle.

32:51.521 --> 32:52.842
I can only do this.

32:59.121 --> 32:59.761
Mother.

33:03.442 --> 33:04.881
I know you just reached home

33:04.882 --> 33:06.741
and it's not the right time
to talk about this.

33:06.742 --> 33:08.082
But I think

33:09.121 --> 33:11.682
it's time for you to settle down.

33:17.521 --> 33:18.362
Do you have

33:19.202 --> 33:20.801
someone you like?

33:25.361 --> 33:28.842
- Marvelous!
- Good!

33:46.242 --> 33:47.442
Eat one, Mother.

33:53.722 --> 33:55.521
Be honest with me.

33:55.642 --> 33:56.961
Is she

33:57.361 --> 33:59.082
Fourth Young Lady Dou?

34:05.002 --> 34:06.520
Young Lady, you're so kind to Mr. Chen.

34:06.521 --> 34:08.801
She risked so much
just to bring him back.

34:09.282 --> 34:11.162
It's not just for Mr. Chen.

34:13.002 --> 34:15.002
For Song Mo and the Duke of Ding,

34:15.521 --> 34:17.361
this is a true injustice.

34:17.902 --> 34:19.861
If I hadn't known,
I would have been better off.

34:19.862 --> 34:22.542
But knowing about this
is hard to ignore.

34:23.541 --> 34:25.482
Where are you getting these ideas from?

34:25.501 --> 34:27.341
It must be Lu Zheng and Lu Ming

34:27.462 --> 34:29.461
who have been exaggerating

34:29.462 --> 34:30.882
and stirring up trouble here.

34:33.221 --> 34:35.381
They're right, though.

34:35.842 --> 34:38.121
Fourth Young Lady Dou is willing
to help you.

34:38.401 --> 34:40.842
So she must be a wise
and principled young woman.

34:41.682 --> 34:43.761
It's just a pity
she was born into the Dou Family.

34:44.362 --> 34:47.042
We can't be sure
she won't be used by her Fifth Uncle.

34:48.502 --> 34:50.561
Fifth Uncle has yet entered
the Grand Secretariat?

34:50.562 --> 34:52.192
Official Wu is still
the Grand Secretary?

34:52.512 --> 34:54.522
(According
to the Records of the Enlightened Age,)

34:54.721 --> 34:56.341
(Mr. Wu clearly took a leave of absence)

34:56.602 --> 34:58.522
(Virtuous Minister)
(to return home this year.)

34:58.792 --> 35:00.552
(Fifth Uncle entered
the Grand Secretariat)

35:00.561 --> 35:01.680
(and gradually took control.)

35:01.681 --> 35:03.000
(Dou Shishu)

35:03.001 --> 35:05.201
(The change of the era name
to Fengming by His Majesty)

35:05.441 --> 35:07.281
(wasn't mentioned in the records too.)

35:08.561 --> 35:10.040
(Could my advice)

35:10.041 --> 35:11.761
(really have changed)

35:11.882 --> 35:13.522
(the course of events?)

35:13.722 --> 35:15.402
(Won't the future be even harder)

35:16.041 --> 35:17.562
(to predict after this?)

35:18.481 --> 35:20.761
There's also the matter of Mr. Wu Shan.

35:22.762 --> 35:24.162
What happened to the Wu Family?

35:26.242 --> 35:29.161
Official Wu cut ties with the Dou Family

35:29.802 --> 35:31.721
to strengthen his own position.

35:32.401 --> 35:36.002
He plans to match make between Dezhen
and the Sixth Young Lady Liang.

35:37.521 --> 35:40.362
(Dezhen is truly in love this time.)

35:40.742 --> 35:42.721
(He has set his sights
on Fourth Young Lady Dou,)

35:43.001 --> 35:44.321
(refusing to give up.)

35:44.322 --> 35:47.402
Even if I'm never destined to be
with Fourth Young Lady Dou in this life,

35:48.242 --> 35:51.042
my feelings for her remain unshakable
and will never change.

35:51.762 --> 35:54.162
I can't marry anyone else
just to please others.

35:57.121 --> 35:58.761
If I don't prune and tend it,

35:59.842 --> 36:01.321
it'll just grow out of shape.

36:02.282 --> 36:03.601
Will the sky not fall

36:04.561 --> 36:06.442
just because you refuse?

36:07.481 --> 36:08.962
If I refuse,

36:09.842 --> 36:13.522
can Meisun come back to life?

36:17.162 --> 36:19.201
Everything else can be negotiated,

36:20.041 --> 36:21.641
but not this.

36:22.802 --> 36:25.122
This is not something
you can decide by will alone.

36:27.121 --> 36:29.560
Dezhen's father passed away early,

36:29.561 --> 36:31.562
and he's always been filial
to his grandfather.

36:31.601 --> 36:32.641
How could this happen?

36:34.401 --> 36:37.281
It looks like he truly loves her.

36:39.081 --> 36:41.002
The Dou Family seeks power and profit.

36:41.401 --> 36:43.442
How could their marriage
be based on love?

36:44.081 --> 36:46.761
Dezhen caught a cold in the rain
and has been burning with a fever,

36:46.762 --> 36:48.162
refusing to seek medical help.

36:48.242 --> 36:49.721
If anything happens to him,

36:50.001 --> 36:51.442
Wu can't bear it.

36:54.282 --> 36:56.801
This situation
is what Dou Shishu wishes for.

36:57.121 --> 36:59.442
Both Dezhen and Wu are stubborn.

36:59.601 --> 37:01.482
I'll figure out a way
to smooth things over.

37:08.601 --> 37:10.522
Mother, time for your medicine.

37:16.762 --> 37:18.601
Father, I'm sorry.

37:18.921 --> 37:20.321
You should learn from Official Dou.

37:20.322 --> 37:23.001
Understand the emperor's will,
and avoid harm for personal gain.

37:23.002 --> 37:24.361
That's the true skill.

37:24.362 --> 37:24.960
I will.

37:24.961 --> 37:27.361
Do you really think
forcing Song Mo to confess

37:27.362 --> 37:29.400
will help you rise to power?

37:29.401 --> 37:32.321
Have you thought about the emperor

37:32.481 --> 37:34.400
and the Grand Secretariat's intentions?

37:34.401 --> 37:35.681
Can we servants decide

37:36.041 --> 37:38.082
who is guilty or innocent?

37:38.601 --> 37:39.761
I understand that now.

37:41.722 --> 37:46.482
The Shadow Guard has already arrived
in Futing to investigate.

37:46.921 --> 37:48.482
I should head there as well.

37:49.601 --> 37:50.881
Until we find the leads

37:50.882 --> 37:52.442
in the Duke of Ding's case,

37:53.242 --> 37:55.402
do not act rashly.

37:55.561 --> 37:56.321
Yes.

38:17.081 --> 38:18.801
What orders do you have for us?

38:21.242 --> 38:22.722
Announce the imperial decree.

38:30.401 --> 38:31.562
These past few days,

38:31.601 --> 38:32.650
first, Grand Secretary Wu

38:32.651 --> 38:33.868
rejected the emperor's decree

38:33.869 --> 38:36.042
to appoint Fifth Master Dou
as Grand Secretary.

38:36.401 --> 38:38.681
Then Mr. Wu Shan refused to marry.

38:39.121 --> 38:40.560
The whole capital knows

38:40.561 --> 38:42.801
that the Wu Family
and the Dou Family are at odds.

38:44.121 --> 38:46.562
Lung abscess is due to infection.

38:46.882 --> 38:49.522
He got soaked in the rain
and refused treatment or medicine.

38:49.762 --> 38:50.522
By the way,

38:50.882 --> 38:52.922
has Imperial Physician Li returned
to the capital?

38:53.001 --> 38:54.120
He is already on his way.

38:54.121 --> 38:55.560
He should be arriving tonight.

38:55.561 --> 38:56.321
Good.

38:59.121 --> 39:01.522
Have you prepared
the gift list I asked for?

39:02.282 --> 39:03.241
Yes.

39:03.762 --> 39:06.321
Chen Qushui has been staying
at Yizhi Hall for a long time.

39:06.362 --> 39:07.296
He probably knows

39:07.297 --> 39:09.641
almost everything about this household.

39:10.601 --> 39:11.922
It doesn't seem right

39:12.121 --> 39:13.321
to let him go like this.

39:15.121 --> 39:16.361
We're not just allies.

39:16.362 --> 39:17.600
She also saved me.

39:17.601 --> 39:19.082
Since I promised her,

39:19.121 --> 39:20.642
I can't go back on my word.

39:22.081 --> 39:23.721
Keeping promises is important.

39:23.842 --> 39:25.761
But Fourth Young Lady and Dou Shishu

39:25.882 --> 39:27.681
seem to be working together.

39:27.842 --> 39:29.402
Just when the good things pass,

39:29.601 --> 39:31.121
trouble follows.

39:31.481 --> 39:33.321
I fear this gentlemen's agreement

39:33.601 --> 39:35.121
can't protect us from treachery.

39:40.162 --> 39:42.082
Grandfather, no need
to persuade me anymore.

39:43.242 --> 39:44.641
A pine tree grows naturally

39:45.401 --> 39:46.962
in the way of life.

39:49.001 --> 39:50.962
But to make it look better,

39:52.282 --> 39:54.082
you would twist its branches with wire,

39:55.121 --> 39:56.721
forcing it into shape.

39:58.601 --> 39:59.601
Grandfather,

40:00.722 --> 40:02.962
is that how you see me too,
a plant you can reshape?

40:03.762 --> 40:07.002
I let you go when you wanted
to be sent out to gain experience.

40:08.041 --> 40:10.202
You are secretly fond of fine woodcraft.

40:10.362 --> 40:12.161
I pretended not to know about it.

40:12.802 --> 40:16.241
When the family was stable,
I could still protect you

40:16.762 --> 40:18.761
when you acted willfully.

40:20.162 --> 40:23.442
But times have changed.

40:25.242 --> 40:29.601
The court is full of new officials,
and predators are everywhere.

40:31.242 --> 40:32.601
If something...

40:35.481 --> 40:37.442
If something happens to me,

40:39.642 --> 40:41.281
who will protect you?

40:43.202 --> 40:45.721
Who will safeguard the Wu Family?

40:46.722 --> 40:48.241
You're giving me no way out!

41:00.561 --> 41:03.201
If you're not fond
of Sixth Young Lady Liang,

41:03.882 --> 41:06.362
I've already shortlisted
a few other noble daughters.

41:07.322 --> 41:08.721
Take your pick,

41:09.722 --> 41:11.402
except the daughters of the Dou Family?

41:11.561 --> 41:13.281
Even if you threaten to end your life,

41:13.282 --> 41:14.641
I won't agree.

41:28.521 --> 41:29.600
This is Physician Li.

41:29.601 --> 41:31.322
He's here to check on Mr. Wu Shan.

41:32.682 --> 41:33.641
Please, follow me.

41:33.642 --> 41:34.842
This way, please.

41:42.612 --> 41:43.841
My apologies for this offense.

41:43.842 --> 41:44.841
Please wait for a moment.

41:44.842 --> 41:46.362
The one in charge will return soon.

41:52.401 --> 41:53.922
The floor is cold.

42:01.202 --> 42:02.161
Grandfather,

42:02.921 --> 42:03.882
do you think

42:05.401 --> 42:07.562
I stopped seeing any physicians
and taking medicine

42:08.081 --> 42:11.281
just to force you into asking
for Fourth Young Lady Dou's hand for me?

42:12.961 --> 42:14.882
She doesn't even have feelings for me.

42:15.921 --> 42:17.641
I just don't want to settle

42:18.561 --> 42:21.042
and use marriage as a way
to secure the family's position.

42:22.041 --> 42:23.641
That would be lying to myself

42:23.642 --> 42:25.362
and hurting someone else!

42:29.401 --> 42:32.042
I only want to break free from this cage

42:33.081 --> 42:34.681
and live true to myself.

42:35.121 --> 42:36.801
Is that really too much to ask?

42:38.162 --> 42:39.882
Do you think of me, your grandfather,

42:42.202 --> 42:43.922
as a cage?

42:45.521 --> 42:46.400
You can't see

42:46.401 --> 42:49.161
how I've been protecting you
from harm every single day.

42:49.162 --> 42:51.801
Do you think fiddling with these things

42:52.081 --> 42:54.402
will make everything go your way?

43:13.001 --> 43:14.201
Fourth Young Lady,

43:14.202 --> 43:15.042
will we ever meet

43:15.081 --> 43:16.522
a fifth time?

43:16.722 --> 43:19.762
Even if your feelings remain the same,
seeing you would still make me happy.

43:19.882 --> 43:21.481
You took advantage of my trust

43:21.482 --> 43:23.001
and tipped off your Fifth Uncle.

43:23.002 --> 43:24.842
Shouldn't I be suspicious of you?

43:25.202 --> 43:31.982
♪The pain of goodbye?♪

43:32.062 --> 43:35.582
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

43:35.902 --> 43:39.422
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

43:39.522 --> 43:45.162
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

43:45.372 --> 43:47.161
♪Where can this restless heart find peace?♪

43:47.162 --> 43:50.301
♪Left alone in an empty hall♪

43:50.302 --> 43:54.022
♪A lifetime chasing fate's lonely call♪

43:54.182 --> 43:58.461
♪Watching seasons fade and storms rise♪

43:58.462 --> 44:01.041
♪It hurts but it's not all for nothing♪

44:01.042 --> 44:02.311
♪My heart is as empty as a quiet street♪

44:02.312 --> 44:05.272
♪Who cares about the path I walk alone?♪

44:05.282 --> 44:09.422
♪Would you take away
the weight of the past?♪

44:09.502 --> 44:11.431
♪Life is fleeting, like morning frost♪

44:11.432 --> 44:14.661
♪Even a moment feels endless with you♪

44:14.662 --> 44:20.882
♪Like a stream flowing steady
through time♪

44:22.762 --> 44:29.572
♪A lone flower falls from the eaves
Moonlight graces steps beneath♪

44:30.132 --> 44:37.322
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

44:37.692 --> 44:40.842
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

44:41.422 --> 44:45.032
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

44:45.152 --> 44:50.912
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

44:51.602 --> 44:52.881
♪In this chaotic world♪

44:52.882 --> 44:55.821
♪Only love lasts♪

44:55.822 --> 44:59.582
♪We'll get through
every challenge together♪

44:59.852 --> 45:04.081
♪No matter how cold
or uncertain the road♪

45:04.082 --> 45:06.661
♪There's nothing to fear
when I'm with you♪

45:06.662 --> 45:07.871
♪My heart feels empty♪

45:07.872 --> 45:10.841
♪But I can hear your voice♪

45:10.842 --> 45:15.061
♪In this life, under moonlight
and across the oceans♪

45:15.062 --> 45:17.432
♪We'll find our way back to each other♪

45:17.562 --> 45:18.411
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:18.412 --> 45:19.311
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:19.312 --> 45:20.301
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)

45:20.302 --> 45:25.752
♪Together, we'll make every moment count♪
